               <head>Grant; Westley, etc.; 30 Ed. III (1356-1357)</head>
               <msContents>
                  <textLang mainLang="la">Latin</textLang>
                  <msItem>
                     <p> 
                        <persName>
                           <forename>Robert</forename> 
                           <surname>Gyffard</surname>
                        </persName> grants and confirms to
                  <persName>
                           <forename>John</forename> de <surname>Brom</surname>
                        </persName>
                  and three others eight acres of land lying in the fields of <placeName key="place_105557">Westley (Westle)</placeName> near 
                  <placeName key="place_104540">Bury St Edmunds (St. Edmund)</placeName>.
                  Dated at <placeName role="date" key="place_105557">Westley (Westle)</placeName> the Tuesday on the feast of St. Crispin and
                  Crispinian, martyrs, <origDate notBefore="1356-01-25" notAfter="1357-01-24">30 Ed. III</origDate>. 
                   
                  </p>
